{
  "texts": [
    "We used the XpertAI tool to suggest structure-property relationships for five case studies in chemistry: (1) the presence of open metal sites in metal-organic frameworks (classification), (2) pore-limiting diameter in metal-organic frameworks (regression), (3) toxicity of small molecules (classification), (4) solubility of small molecules (regression), and (5) upper flammability limit of organic molecules (regression).",
    "Please note that we used the SHAP method as the chosen XAI method and its default hyperparameters to generate NLEs in the following case studies.",
    "We chose the SHAP method due to its consistency in generating global explanations in comparison to LIME.",
    "Complete NLEs and SHAP plots for each case study from XpertAI are provided in Appendices A and E in SI respectively.",
    "A set of published articles was uploaded for each case study to draw scientific evidence."
  ]
}